@startuml Electron业务架构图
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Electron 业务架构图 (TOGAF Business Architecture)

package "业务目标层" {
  [提供跨平台桌面应用开发框架] as BusinessGoal
  [降低桌面应用开发门槛] as Goal1
  [统一Web技术与原生能力] as Goal2
  [支持快速迭代和部署] as Goal3
}

package "利益相关者" {
  [开发者] as Stakeholder1
  [最终用户] as Stakeholder2
  [维护团队] as Stakeholder3
  [开源社区] as Stakeholder4
}

package "业务流程" {
  [应用开发流程] as Process1
  [构建打包流程] as Process2
  [分发部署流程] as Process3
  [运行维护流程] as Process4
}

package "业务能力" {
  [跨平台支持能力] as Capability1
  [原生API集成能力] as Capability2
  [Web技术栈能力] as Capability3
  [安全隔离能力] as Capability4
  [性能优化能力] as Capability5
}

package "价值主张" {
  [快速开发] as Value1
  [代码复用] as Value2
  [原生体验] as Value3
  [生态丰富] as Value4
}

' 业务目标关系
BusinessGoal --> Goal1
BusinessGoal --> Goal2
BusinessGoal --> Goal3

' 利益相关者与业务目标
Stakeholder1 --> BusinessGoal : 使用框架开发应用
Stakeholder2 --> BusinessGoal : 使用桌面应用
Stakeholder3 --> BusinessGoal : 维护框架
Stakeholder4 --> BusinessGoal : 贡献代码

' 业务流程关系
Process1 --> Process2 : 开发完成
Process2 --> Process3 : 构建完成
Process3 --> Process4 : 部署完成

' 业务能力支持业务流程
Capability1 --> Process1 : 支持多平台开发
Capability2 --> Process1 : 提供原生API
Capability3 --> Process1 : 使用Web技术
Capability4 --> Process4 : 保障安全
Capability5 --> Process4 : 优化性能

' 价值主张
Value1 --> Capability3 : 基于Web技术
Value2 --> Capability1 : 跨平台复用
Value3 --> Capability2 : 原生能力
Value4 --> Capability3 : 丰富生态

' 利益相关者获得价值
Stakeholder1 --> Value1
Stakeholder1 --> Value2
Stakeholder2 --> Value3
Stakeholder1 --> Value4

note right of BusinessGoal
  Electron的核心业务目标：
  让开发者能够使用Web技术
  构建跨平台桌面应用
end note

note right of Process1
  应用开发流程包括：
  - 编写主进程代码
  - 编写渲染进程代码
  - 配置应用元数据
end note

note right of Capability1
  跨平台支持：
  - macOS
  - Windows
  - Linux
end note

@enduml

